rows.label: qst202915_msg0001
rows.name:
You sure you want to just stand
there smilin'?

rows.label: qst202915_msg0002
rows.name:
This girl's a proper go-getter.
If you're not careful, she might steal
me away from you someday!

rows.label: qst202915_msg0003
rows.name:
Well, I wouldn't want that...
But I think it'll be fine.

rows.label: qst202915_msg0004
rows.name:
Like you said, your Driver's tough
enough to take a challenge!

rows.label: qst202915_msg0005
rows.name:
Well, that doesn't sound great...
But don't you worry!

rows.label: qst202915_msg0006
rows.name:
You said it yourself - I'm tough
enough to take any challenge!

rows.label: qst202915_msg0007
rows.name:
That would be quite problematic,
but I see no reason to worry.

rows.label: qst202915_msg0008
rows.name:
After all, it is as you say. Your Driver
is tough enough to take any challenge!

rows.label: qst202915_msg0009
rows.name:
That would be a pain, but don't
you worry yourself!

rows.label: qst202915_msg0010
rows.name:
Like you said, your Driver's tough!
I can handle the challenge!

rows.label: qst202915_msg0011
rows.name:
Hahah... I did say that, didn't I?
I guess I can rest easy, then!

rows.label: qst202915_msg0012
rows.name:
Let's make this partnership
a long and fruitful one!
